    adding children at the start or end sides by specifying “start” or “end” as
    the “type” attribute of a ``<child>`` element, or setting the center widget
    by specifying “center” value.

    # CSS nodes

    .. code-block:: text

        actionbar
        ╰── revealer
            ╰── box
                ├── box.start
                │   ╰── [start children]
                ├── [center widget]
                ╰── box.end
                    ╰── [end children]

