    destroying your text widget:

    .. code-block:: c

        static void
        my_widget_dispose (GObject *object)
        {
          ...
          :meth:`Gtk.Editable.finish_delegate` (GTK_EDITABLE (self));
          g_clear_pointer (&self->text_widget, :meth:`Gtk.Widget.unparent`);
          ...
