    - To select a file for opening, use :data:`Gtk.FileChooserAction.OPEN`.

    - To save a file for the first time, use :data:`Gtk.FileChooserAction.SAVE`,
      and suggest a name such as “Untitled” with
      :meth:`Gtk.FileChooser.set_current_name`.

    - To save a file under a different name, use :data:`Gtk.FileChooserAction.SAVE`,
      and set the existing file with :meth:`Gtk.FileChooser.set_file`.

    - To choose a folder instead of a file, use :data:`Gtk.FileChooserAction.SELECT_FOLDER`.

