    see the :class:`Gtk.FileChooserDialog` documentation.

    ## Response Codes

    :class:`Gtk.FileChooserNative` inherits from :class:`Gtk.NativeDialog`,
    which means it will return :data:`Gtk.ResponseType.ACCEPT` if the user accepted,
    and :data:`Gtk.ResponseType.CANCEL` if he pressed cancel. It can also return
    :data:`Gtk.ResponseType.DELETE_EVENT` if the window was unexpectedly closed.

