    Although a :class:`Gtk.FlowBox` must have only :class:`Gtk.FlowBoxChild` children, you
    can add any kind of widget to it via :meth:`Gtk.FlowBox.insert`, and a
    :class:`Gtk.FlowBoxChild` widget will automatically be inserted between the box
    and the widget.

