    .. code-block:: text

        flowbox
        ├── flowboxchild
        │   ╰── <child>
        ├── flowboxchild
        │   ╰── <child>
        ┊
        ╰── [rubberband]

    :class:`Gtk.FlowBox` uses a single CSS node with name flowbox. :class:`Gtk.FlowBoxChild`
    uses a single CSS node with name flowboxchild. For rubberband selection,
    a subnode with name rubberband is used.

