class ListView(ListBase, Accessible, Buildable, ConstraintTarget, Orientable, Scrollable):
    """
    Presents a large dynamic list of items.

    :class:`Gtk.ListView` uses its factory to generate one row widget for each visible
    item and shows them in a linear display, either vertically or horizontally.

    The :attr:`Gtk.ListView.show-separators` property offers a simple way to
    display separators between the rows.

    :class:`Gtk.ListView` allows the user to select items according to the selection
    characteristics of the model. For models that allow multiple selected items,
    it is possible to turn on _rubberband selection_, using
    :attr:`Gtk.ListView.enable-rubberband`.

