    :class:`Gtk.Popover` supports the following keyboard shortcuts:

    - <kbd>Escape</kbd> closes the popover.
    - <kbd>Alt</kbd> makes the mnemonics visible.

    The following signals have default keybindings:

    - ``Gtk.Popover::activate-default``

    # CSS nodes

    .. code-block:: text

        popover.background[.menu]
        ├── arrow
        ╰── contents
            ╰── <child>

    :class:`Gtk.Popover` has a main node with name ``popover``, an arrow with name ``arrow``,
