    Until GTK 4.10, :class:`Gtk.TreeExpander` used the :class:`Gtk.AccessibleRole.group` role.

    Since GTK 4.12, :class:`Gtk.TreeExpander` uses the :class:`Gtk.AccessibleRole.button` role.
