    model, the next example will be a callback for the :class:`Gtk.TreeSelection`
    :class:`Gtk.TreeSelection`::changed` signal.  In this callback, we get a string
    from COLUMN_1 of the model.  We then modify the string, find the same
    selected row on the child model, and change the row there.

