        from inside its implementation of the :meth:`Gtk.Widget.do_size_allocate`
        virtual method. Calls to :meth:`Gtk.Widget.queue_resize` from inside
        :meth:`Gtk.Widget.do_size_allocate` will be silently ignored.

        This function is only for use in widget implementations.
        """
