        properties
        :attr:`Gtk.Widget.margin-start`,
        :attr:`Gtk.Widget.margin-end`,
        :attr:`Gtk.Widget.margin-top`, and
        :attr:`Gtk.Widget.margin-bottom`, but it does include pretty
        much all other padding or border properties set by any subclass
        of :class:`Gtk.Widget`.
