        false for :class:`Gtk.DirectionType.tab-forward` and
        :class:`Gtk.DirectionType.tab-backward`. For the other values
        of :class:`Gtk.DirectionType` it returns true.

        Whenever the default handler returns true, it also calls
        :meth:`Gtk.Widget.error_bell` to notify the user of the
        failed keyboard navigation.

